Dear Colleagues,

As we have discussed during the meeting in Manchester, the book is now
fully in progress. Minor changes concern the format (lprocl.sty from
WS), see the home page http://www.phy.umist.ac.uk/MASLN/. I have also
links to subroutines for the AV8' and MS3 potentials on that page, so
that we can have a common set of potentials with which to benchmark our
methods.
We look forward to your timely contributions.

